{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/rotatestomatchcamera"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and the map is rotated, the annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view rotates. This is also the behavior of ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"reference"},{"text":" objects. When the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" the annotation has its rotation angle fixed.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". Set this property to "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s rotation is important."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","title":"rotatesToMatchCamera","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L193"},"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)rotatesToMatchCamera","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"identifier"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/rotatesToMatchCamera","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view rotates together","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with the map.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationImage","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by the map view.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/rotatesToMatchCamera":{"fragments":[{"text":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"rotatesToMatchCamera","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/rotatestomatchcamera","abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view rotates together","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with the map.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/rotatesToMatchCamera"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"title":"MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"role":"symbol"}}}